name: Automatically Load and Close LTL Retail
command:
list warehouses
|
process dss ltl shipment auto load and close
 where ordtyp_list = 'SR,MR,OT,SO,NFT,DCT,ECS,CUO,RTV,SC,ZRP'
   and wh_id = @wh_id
